idhu enna maayam ( english : what magic is this ? ) is a 2015 indian tamil romantic comedy film written and directed by a. l. vijay and produced by r. sarathkumar , radhika sarathkumar and listin stephen under the production banner of magic frames .   the film features vikram prabhu and keerthy suresh in the lead roles , while g. v. prakash kumar composes the film 's music .   production began for the film in august 2014 and released in july 2015 .